class Solution {
    public boolean canConstruct(String s, int k) {
        int[] charCount = new int[26];
        for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {
            charCount[c - 'a']++;
        }
        int oddCount = 0;
        for (int count : charCount) {
            if (count % 2 != 0) {
                oddCount++;
            }
        }
        return k <= s.length() - oddCount + (oddCount > 0 ? 1 : 0);
    }
}
```

efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(n)
space complexity: O(1)
